## Inputs and Outputs

### Inputs

| Input | Source | Description |
|-------|--------|-------------|
| MIDI messages | Hardware/Network MIDI devices | Note On/Off, CC, PC, Sysex |
| Device selection | User/UI | Which MIDI device to use |
| Mapping config | Presets/UI | MIDI → parameter bindings |
| Learning requests | UI | MIDI learn capture mode |

### Outputs

| Output | Destination | Description |
|--------|-------------|-------------|
| Parameter updates | VJLive3 parameters | Real-time control values |
| MIDI feedback | Controller devices | LED, display, motor feedback |
| Mapping events | UI, Logging | Mapping changes, learning |
| Device status | Monitoring | Connection state, errors |

