## What It Does NOT Do

- ❌ Does **not** generate audio (use AudioEngine)
- ❌ Does **not** control DMX directly (use DMXEngine)
- ❌ Does **not** provide visual effects (use EffectEngine)
- ❌ Does **not** handle OSC input (use OSCController)
- ❌ Does **not** store show data (use ShowControl)
- ❌ Does **not** manage user permissions (use Auth)

