## Success Criteria

### Must Pass (All Required)

- [ ] FPS ≥ 58 when MIDI active
- [ ] All unit tests pass (≥80% coverage)
- [ ] MIDI input latency < 1ms
- [ ] MIDI output latency < 1ms
- [ ] Supports at least 10 different MIDI controllers
- [ ] MIDI learn works reliably (captures within 5 seconds)
- [ ] Thread-safe: no race conditions in message handling
- [ ] Hot-plugging detection within 500ms

### Should Pass (Best Effort)

- [ ] Support for 20+ controllers simultaneously
- [ ] rtpMIDI network MIDI support
- [ ] Advanced mapping (conditions, macros, scripts)
