## Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|------------|--------|------------|
| MIDI device compatibility | Medium | Medium | Test with popular controllers, fallback drivers |
| Latency too high | Low | High | Real-time thread priority, lock-free queues |
| Thread safety issues | Low | High | Atomic operations, careful locking |
| Memory leaks from device handles | Low | Medium | Reference counting, cleanup |
| Platform differences (Windows/Linux/macOS) | Medium | Medium | Abstract backend, CI on all platforms |

